	"description": [
		{
			"type": "paragraph",
			"text": "<span class='text-color-green'>DeadFrame2D</span> is a lightweight and modular 2D game engine written in C++, designed for rapid prototyping and high-performance game development."
		},
		{
			"type": "paragraph",
			"text": "It leverages popular libraries like <span class='text-color-green'>SDL2</span> for rendering and input, <span class='text-color-green'>Box2D</span> for physics, and uses a <span class='text-color-green'>Premake</span>-based build system to simplify cross-platform setup."
		},
		{
			"type": "paragraph",
			"text": "The engine is organized for modular development and includes a template project that helps developers get started quickly with a clean structure and build scripts for both <span class='text-color-green'>Windows</span> and <span class='text-color-green'>Linux</span>."
		},
		{
			"type": "paragraph",
			"text": "Key features include:"
		},
		{
			"type": "list",
			"items": [
				"üé• Camera-based rendering.",
				"‚öôÔ∏è Physics-based collisions via Box2D.",
				"üß± Scene and ECS architecture.",
				"üéÆ Controller and keyboard/mouse input support.",
				"üó∫Ô∏è Tilemap rendering with <a href=\"https://www.mapeditor.org/\" class=\"link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Tiled</a> support.",
				"‚è≥ Coroutines.",
				"üß† Event-driven memory and object management.",
				"üêû Debug mode with visual overlays.",
				"üîß Cross-platform setup with Premake.<span class='medium-line-break'></span>"
			]
		},
		{
			"type": "paragraph",
			"text": "I used this engine to develop the following games:"
		},
		{
			"type": "list",
			"items": [
				"<a href=\"https://github.com/Adamska-01/Bobble_Blast/\" class=\"link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">BobbleBlast</a> - a classic puzzle-style bubble shooter.",
				"<a href=\"https://github.com/Adamska-01/Retro_Platformer/\" class=\"link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Retro Platformer</a> - a platform demo inspired by Super Mario."
			]
		},
		{
			"type": "paragraph",
			"text": "These demonstrate the engine's flexibility for different game genres."
		},
		{
			"type": "paragraph",
			"text": "Development is ongoing and guided by a structured <a href=\"https://excalidraw.com/#json=MwfqT_r168ImA-rdfvIns,DPgS7jd4DRs6UnH7zHazqw\" class=\"link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Roadmap</a> that outlines upcoming improvements and planned features."
		}
